        "en": "Intel Unveils Xeon Scalable Processor with Integrated AI Accelerators for Data Centers"
      },
      "url": "https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2026/04/18/intel-launches-xeon-scalable-ai/",
      "summary": {
        "original": "Intel launched its latest Xeon Scalable processor family, featuring built-in AI accelerators that deliver up to 2x performance improvement for machine learning workloads compared to the previous generation. The new chips also support DDR5 memory and PCIe 5.0, targeting cloud providers and enterprise data centers seeking to reduce reliance on discrete GPUs for AI inference.",
        "ko": "인텔은 최신 제온 스케일러블 프로세서 제품군을 출시했으며, 내장된 AI 가속기를 통해 이전 세대 대비 머신러닝 워크로드 성능을 최대 2배 향상시켰습니다. 새로운 칩은 DDR5 메모리와 PCIe 5.0도 지원하며, 클라우드 제공업체와 엔터프라이즈 데이터센터가 AI 추론을 위해 별도 GPU에 의존하는 것을 줄일 수 있도록 대상으로 합니다.",
        "ja": "インテルは最新のXeonスケーラブルプロセッサーファミリーを発売し、内蔵されたAIアクセレーターにより前世代と比較して機械学習ワークロードのパフォーマンスを最大2倍向上させました。新しいチップはDDR5メモリとPCIe 5.0もサポートしており、クラウドプロバイダーやエンタープライズデータセンターがAI推論のために離散GPUに依存する必要を減らすことを対象としています。",
        "en": "Intel launched its latest Xeon Scalable processor family, featuring built-in AI accelerators that deliver up to 2x performance improvement for machine learning workloads compared to the previous generation. The new chips also support DDR5 memory and PCIe 5.0, targeting cloud providers and enterprise data centers seeking to reduce reliance on discrete GPUs for AI inference."
